data.description: Brand new custom Metal roof,flat roof and gutters just put on (12/23) .Opportunity Unlimited possibilty for mother in law suite or rental income. Small beach town w/big seaside charm! This beautiful property is light & bright, open concept kitchen, gas stove, reverse osmosis water system, newer high-end appliances & more! Extensive upgrades/renovations in the last few years, including new flooring throughout, new kitchen, bathrooms,IMPACT windows & doors, tankless water heater & the list goes on. Featuring a large living/bonus room with its own separate entrance. Plenty of storage outside w/two custom storage sheds with power. The backyard is an entertainer’s dream with a heated saltwater pool & hot tub nestled amongst lush landscaping and no maintenance artificial turf
